From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: OpenPhone <openphone@example.invalid>
Date: Mon, 1 Jun 2026 19:10:00 +0300
Subject: [PATCH] OpenPhone: add Settings-hosted audit and grant pages

Add Settings-owned OpenPhone subpages for task-grant policy and framework audit status.
The audit page reads the OpenPhone framework service directly when available and keeps
the assistant export flow as a handoff for file generation.
---
